[Music]

383
00:22:38,333 --> 00:22:48,250
[Music]

384
00:22:48,333 --> 00:22:58,250
[Music]

385
00:22:58,333 --> 00:23:08,291
[Music]

386
00:23:08,375 --> 00:23:18,291
[Music]

387
00:23:18,375 --> 00:23:31,666
[Music]

388
00:23:56,666 --> 00:23:58,083
Hold on...

389
00:23:58,166 --> 00:24:00,708
They're gonna use magic
to call down an angel...?

390
00:24:00,791 --> 00:24:03,250
Is that what it will
take to heal Index?

391
00:24:03,333 --> 00:24:05,208
Next time, "Necessarius."

